<h2 id="4-progress-is-non-linear">4. Progress is non-linear.</h2>

<p>In my first few months, I experienced the phenomenon called â€˜beginner gainsâ€™, where I went up 5 lbs on my lifts every workout. Gaining strength is a lot harder to come by now.</p>

